Architecture Summary
Both systems are fundamentally well-designed at the macro level: clean broker abstraction, proper async event loop usage, circuit breaker on broker calls, state persistence across restarts, and a working reconnect strategy. The issues above are fixable in isolation without a rewrite. Fix the three critical live-trading bugs (H3, H4, H8) before any further live deployments, and rotate your API keys immediately.
